            background-color: rgb(44, 245, 215);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1em;
        }

        nav {
            background-color: #eee;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section {
            padding: 2em;
            text-align: center;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Travel to Antarctica</h1>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="#about">About</a> |
        <a href="#places">Places to Visit</a> |
        <a href="#tips">Travel Tips</a>
    </nav>

    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Antarctica</h2>
        <p>Antarctica is the southernmost continent and is known for its breathtaking landscapes, unique wildlife, and extreme conditions. Explore the beauty of the frozen continent!</p>
    </section>

    <section id="places">
        <h2>Places to Visit</h2>
        <p>Discover amazing places such as the Antarctic Peninsula, Ross Ice Shelf, and the South Pole. Each destination offers a unique experience and stunning scenery.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="tips">
        <h2>Travel Tips</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Bring warm clothing and layers.</li>
            <li>Stay hydrated at high altitudes.</li>
            <li>Respect the local wildlife and environment.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

</body>
